    <preface id="target" revision="1">
        <title>Target Audience</title>
        <para>
            This guide is intended for Java developers who are interested in Object Relational Mapping using Reladomo.
        </para>
    </preface>

    <part label="I">
        <title>Reladomo Basics</title>
        <partintro>
            <para>
                This part introduces the basics of Reladomo. It includes basic domain modellimg concepts, domain modeling in Relaomo and a high
                level overview of various Reladomo features. Finally, all of these comcepts are used to
                implement a REST API for a bank where the data is persisted and fetched using Reladomo.
            </para>
            <para>
                The code for all the chapters in this part can be found in <code>simple-bank</code> Maven module.
            </para>
        </partintro>
